## 🔹 Feature 1: Multi-Configuration Testing

System must:

* Run same workload on:

  * no security
  * TLS
  * mTLS

---

## 🔹 Feature 2: Multiple Workloads

You MUST vary:

* message size
* throughput rate

Example:

| Scenario | Messages/sec | Size  |
| -------- | ------------ | ----- |
| Low      | 1k/s         | 1KB   |
| Medium   | 10k/s        | 10KB  |
| High     | 50k/s        | 100KB |

---

